{"tid":1859054,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要再叫「解散警隊，刻不容緩」。嘗試叫「解散防暴，刻不容緩」","createTime":"2020-02-03T05:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T10:46:35.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d45a2daafb8ad3abda72e5569d56174dfc3a991b","tid":1859054,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"防暴警察：防暴的職責是組織、部署、訓練和裝備以應對群眾、抗議或騷亂的警察。 防暴警察可能是在特定情況下擔任防暴警察角色的常規警察，或者他們可能是在正規警察部隊內或與其並行組織的單獨部隊。防暴警察用於各種不同的情況，並用於各種不同目的。<br />\n<br />\n警察：警察的主要職責為執法、 維持公共安全及保障財產。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，一個城市，警察係必要的，但防暴非必要。市民需要警察，但不需要防暴警察。"},{"pid":"ca8798a1381e756828aea7647b3866277cf1682e","tid":1859054,"uid":17802,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"細路仔賓周 愈玩愈縮。 不如直接宣佈抗爭結束算啦。反正依家都止暴制亂成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bc4af09ad8a7165f316303d7e9f77d7f6ea124","tid":1859054,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"參見：警察與防暴警察的分別<br />\n<br />\n警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=7f62bafb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n防暴警察（鎮壓暴動的警察部隊）<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=579a1240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%